			<div id="post-3498" class="post-3498 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-videos-2 tag-federal-reserve tag-national-debt">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/monetary-myths-and-the-debt-ceiling" title="Permalink to Monetary Myths and the Debt Ceiling" rel="bookmark">Monetary Myths and the Debt Ceiling</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/monetary-myths-and-the-debt-ceiling" title="3:28 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">January 14, 2011</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/monetary-myths-and-the-debt-ceiling#comments" title="Comment on Monetary Myths and the Debt Ceiling">18 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<div id="tweetbutton3498" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fmonetary-myths-and-the-debt-ceiling&amp;text=Monetary%20Myths%20and%20the%20Debt%20Ceiling&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fmonetary-myths-and-the-debt-ceiling" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><p>Right now the congress is supposedly &#8220;debating raising the debt ceiling&#8221;.  This video explains&#8230;</p>
<ul>
<li>Why the debate isn&#8217;t a debate and nothing but political theater</li>
<li>Why they will and must raise the ceiling under the current system</li>
<li>Why we can never pay off the national debt with the current system</li>
<li>Why those calling to not raise the ceiling probably don&#8217;t know what they are asking for</li>
</ul>
<p>Of course I am for elimination of the national debt but capping the debt in a system where money is debt just simply isn&#8217;t possible.</p>
<p><object classid="clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000" width="600" height="362" codebase="http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0"><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true" /><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always" /><param name="src" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/-HtqCsFpXw4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US&amp;color1=0x234900&amp;color2=0x4e9e00" /><param name="allowfullscreen" value="true" /><embed type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="600" height="362" src="http://www.youtube.com/v/-HtqCsFpXw4?fs=1&amp;hl=en_US&amp;color1=0x234900&amp;color2=0x4e9e00" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object></p>
