			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/basic-financial-we-never-get-in-school" title="Permalink to Episode-434- The Basic Financial Education We Never Get in School" rel="bookmark">Episode-434- The Basic Financial Education We Never Get in School</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/basic-financial-we-never-get-in-school" title="12:27 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">May 13, 2010</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/basic-financial-we-never-get-in-school#comments" title="Comment on Episode-434- The Basic Financial Education We Never Get in School">6 Comments</a></span>
