			<div id="post-1808" class="post-1808 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-banking tag-citi tag-economy tag-federal-reserve tag-general-motors tag-government-bailout">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-427-the-economic-shell-game-continues" title="Permalink to Episode-427- The Economic Shell Game Continues" rel="bookmark">Episode-427- The Economic Shell Game Continues</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-427-the-economic-shell-game-continues" title="11:15 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">April 29, 2010</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-427-the-economic-shell-game-continues#comments" title="Comment on Episode-427- The Economic Shell Game Continues">5 Comments</a></span>
